 The syntax doesn't change how it works.

00:01:04.760 --> 00:01:07.240
 This is how it really works.

00:01:07.240 --> 00:01:09.660
 And the things that's super excellent about this

00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:11.720
 is that it uses the function keyword.

