 And again, we have a curly brace to start it.

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:45.720
 And the thing that's different

00:01:45.720 --> 00:01:47.780
 is there's this notion of this.

00:01:47.780 --> 00:01:51.000
 So we make sort of an empty vessel

