 And then by running the code,

00:01:56.720 --> 00:01:58.600
 we're actually populating that empty vessel.

00:01:58.600 --> 00:02:03.600
 So this.x is going to create a member variable

00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:06.600
 called x inside this,

00:02:06.600 --> 00:02:09.240
 which is the empty vessel object that we're creating.

00:02:09.240 --> 00:02:11.360
 And then we're gonna fill up, okay?

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:13.440
 And then we have this.party.

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:19.480
 This.party is also a piece of data in the this object

