 Create an empty object,

00:03:56.200 --> 00:03:58.540
 and then use the party animal code

00:03:58.540 --> 00:04:00.140
 to sort of fill out that object

00:04:00.140 --> 00:04:02.080
 with a bit of code and a bit of data.

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:04.260
 And so that says, run all this,

00:04:04.260 --> 00:04:05.940
 but instead of just running it,

00:04:05.940 --> 00:04:09.000
 give me back the thing that eventually it produces.

