 that we're in the constructor, okay?

00:08:07.960 --> 00:08:10.400
 And the purpose of the constructor in object orientation

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:14.360
 is to set the initial conditions of the object

00:08:14.360 --> 00:08:17.080
 so that the object is ready to be used.

